snippet.title: Rainbow Six® Extraction: PlayStation® Showcase 2021 | World Trailer
snippet.description:
For decades, Team Rainbow has been the shield against the worst global threats imaginable: hostage situations, biological weapons, the threat of nuclear war. But now, we face the greatest terror our world has ever known: a lethal, mutating alien threat. 

Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six Extraction will be available in January 2022 on PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X | S, Xbox One, Stadia and PC.
For more info: 
www.rainbowsixextraction.com
